    <div class="summary-box">
      <strong>Quick Summary — Key Takeaways</strong>
      <ul>
        <li>The University of Florida Online ranks #1 for 2026 with in-state tuition as low as $129/credit.</li>
        <li>Online degrees are on average $31,165 cheaper than in-person equivalents at public universities.</li>
        <li>85% of institutions now view online learning as a strategic priority for student access.</li>
