      <li><a href="https://collegescorecard.ed.gov/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">College Scorecard</a> — Graduate earnings and student debt data</li>
      <li><a href="https://petersonsdata.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Peterson's Database</a> — Program offerings and admissions requirements</li>
      <li><a href="https://nces.ed.gov/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">National Center for Education Statistics</a> — Accreditation and institutional profiles</li>
    </ul>

